HEADWORD: Ruiniform
<hw>Ru"in*i*form</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Ruin</ets>
+ <ets>-form</ets>: cf. F. <ets>ruiniforme</ets>.]</ety> <def>Having the
